string replaceSubstring(string input, string target, string replacement) {
    string result = "";
    int n = input.length();
    int m = target.length();

    for (int i = 0; i < n; ) {
        // Check substring match
        if (i + m <= n && input.substr(i, m) == target) {
            result += replacement;
            i += m; // move window by target length
        } else {
            result += input[i];
            i++;
        }
    }
    return result;
}

⏱ Time & Space Complexity

Time: O(n × m)
(n = input length, m = target length)

Space: O(n) (new result string)
